title: ALPHA Sydney Diamond+ LFM *Repost*
body:
Alpha Sydney is nearing trialing date so this will be the last call for any other high ranking League players that wants a shot into our Diamond team. The date and time for the trials will be at _**Tuesday 6PM**_ This will mean that the cut off for the applicants will be then.

Moving on to the point at hand, this post is calling for any Analysts that is willing to put in the time and effort to help guide our team for better results. We will be looking at past experience however will be pretty open to new and upcoming Analysts. If you are interested on either of these rolls, please add in game Kumdozer1 or just reply directly to this thread. Thank you for reading.
